    <item>
      <title>比亚迪暂停墨西哥工厂建设计划直至美国大选结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-04/byd-pauses-mexico-factory-plans-until-after-us-election-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据称，比亚迪将暂停其墨西哥电动汽车工厂计划，至少要等到美国总统大选结束后，因为在美国政策转变的情况下，该公司采取了观望态度。彭博社的 Danny Lee 报道。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-04/byd-pauses-mexico-factory-plans-until-after-us-election-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 03:48:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>托克与 MinRes 达成 4 亿美元现金换铁矿石交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/trafigura-struck-400-million-cash-for-iron-ore-deal-with-minres</link>
      <description><![CDATA[托克集团与矿产资源公司达成了一项价值 4 亿美元的铁矿石预付款协议，由于两大主要大宗商品价格低迷，这家澳大利亚矿业公司专注于保留现金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/trafigura-struck-400-million-cash-for-iron-ore-deal-with-minres</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 03:30:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>路易达孚收购 Namoi Cotton 的要约获得 FIRB 批准</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/louis-dreyfus-gets-firb-approval-for-namoi-cotton-takeover-bid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[路易达孚集团表示，其对纳莫伊棉花 (Namoi Cotton) 的收购提议已获得澳大利亚外国投资审查委员会的批准，此前纳莫伊棉花同意采取措施缓解竞争担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/louis-dreyfus-gets-firb-approval-for-namoi-cotton-takeover-bid</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 03:20:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Nvidia 惨败拖累亚洲股市：下一步如何？</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-04/nvidia-rout-pulls-down-asian-stocks-what-s-next</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英伟达公司遭遇创纪录的 2790 亿美元暴跌，导致美国股市下跌，半导体股领跌亚洲各大股指。美国司法部向英伟达和其他公司发出传票，寻求该芯片制造商违反反垄断法的证据。市场专家在彭博电视台发表看法。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-04/nvidia-rout-pulls-down-asian-stocks-what-s-next</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 03:15:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
