    <item>
      <title>原油供应过剩担忧加剧，WTI 价格重回 60 美元左右</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-sept-4</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于利比亚政治动乱可能缓解，市场焦点重新转向 OPEC+ 的增产计划，同时需求担忧依然存在，油价在周二下跌近 5% 后继续走低。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-sept-4</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 23:31:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度官员将 Byju 的贷方从债权人小组中除名</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/byju-s-lenders-kicked-off-creditor-panel-by-india-court-official</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度法院指定的仲裁员将 Byju’s 的美国债权人从有影响力的债权人委员会中剔除，这对于陷入困境、试图避免破产的在线教育公司来说是一个潜在的福音。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/byju-s-lenders-kicked-off-creditor-panel-by-india-court-official</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 21:57:55 GMT</pubDate>
